input_str: Windows Internet Explorer enterprise compatibility mode, enhancements for keyboard and mouse users, pin modern apps to the taskbar, release of Windows 8.1 version supported by Bing, many other free services for non-Windows 8.1/8 OS users etc. According to Microsoft, Windows 8.1 Update 1-Spring 2014 RTM has already been issued to OEM partners and Windows 8.1 users can download it
